Distributed Link Tracking Client<br>
Distributed Transaction Coordinator<br>
Help and Support<br>
IMAPI CD-Burning COM Service** (only if do you not use the cd-rw xp record support)<br>
IPSEC Services<br>
Logical Disk Manager Administrative Service<br>
MS Software Shadow Copy Provider<br>
Net Logon<br>
NetMeeting Remote Desktop Sharing<br>
Network DDE<br>
Network DDE DSDM<br>
Network Location Awareness (NLA)<br>
